  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Weekend work to activate Operation Brock
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Details of work taking place on the M20 in Kent this weekend to activate Operation Brock have been confirmed today by Highways England (Friday 25 October).</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 25 October 2019
</div>

